      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=deq7qz65l2]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=deq7qz65l2]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=c6isxt0kyc]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=c6isxt0kyc]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ccjvqrmvyj]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ccjvqrmvyj]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=asbtwae93j]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=asbtwae93j]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ud6sort1mw]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ud6sort1mw]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" width=\"102\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700944/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743661561684&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/405700944/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1743661561684&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"73\" data-width=\"59\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"405733559\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"405700944\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"d8b469b1-5a69-4bf9-9917-6bc1bf6d814c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/405700944/RenderManUniversit